// Demonstrates generating a complete web application structure

// Codex CLI prompt: "Create a React 18 dashboard application with Vite, 
// TypeScript, React Query for data fetching, Tailwind CSS styling, 
// Jest and React Testing Library for tests, and a Node.js/Express 
// backend with Prisma ORM, PostgreSQL, and JWT authentication. 
// Include a user authentication flow with login/logout/register pages."

